headline: RDN Q4 Earnings Beat on Higher Premiums, Net Investment Income
summary: Radian Group's Q4 results reflect improved investment income, higher revenues across both the Mortgage and All Other segments as well as lower higher expenses.

headline: The Hartford Unveils Refreshed Brand With Modernized Stag Logo
summary: HARTFORD, Conn., February 06, 2025--The Hartford launched its new brand, featuring a bold, contemporary look for its iconic stag logo that honors the company’s rich history while demonstrating its modern, visionary spirit.
